title: Noahs Rump
text: Noahs Rump is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in the <a href="Central%20New%20York">Central New York</a> region of <a href="New%20York%20%28state%29">New York</a>. It is located southwest of <a href="Plainfield%2C%20New%20York%23Communities%20and%20locations%20in%20Plainfield">Plainfield Center, New York</a>.
